data.description: Explore the unique "Round House". Nestled on a serene 1.68-acre property filled with fruit trees and seasonal hops, this circular home provides a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. The distinctive round exterior footprint of the home creates a unique floor plan, providing for a one-of-a-kind living experience. Propane heating, a shared well, and a generator connection ensure that seasonal power outages are never a concern. The property also includes an expansive 1200+ square foot shop complete with a woodstove to keep you warm all year round. Previously the site of a small local auto shop, the hydraulic car lift is still available for use. Don't miss the opportunity to make this unique property your own!
